{"tid":1787111,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【迎2020】為免大量人群聚集 旅發局取消除夕煙花匯演 改辦煙火版「幻彩詠香江」","createTime":"2019-12-17T16:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T14:57:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1258be19217d6653418a72bf394fb4709d1f49","tid":1787111,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:09:34.000Z","msg":"驚心動魄的2019年尚有兩星期就過去，迎接2020年，但今年的除夕（31日）「失色」。持續逾半年的反修例示威衝突仍未平息，旅遊發展局經審視後，為免出現大量人群聚集，決定取消今年除夕煙花匯演，改為在元旦凌晨0時上演升級版「幻彩詠香江」，屆時維港兩旁部分大廈天台亦將發放煙火。<br />\n<br />\n不過旅發局亦希望市民可以同慶2020年到來，將推出倒數手機程式及大抽獎活動，獎品逾萬份，詳情明日（19日）公布。"},{"pid":"66d476cd03749e8d7409fd1784a974822cc8ebeb","tid":1787111,"uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"加tg"},{"pid":"cf3a3037b187b2d433d9d03c2a0471e1b467156c","tid":1787111,"uid":258258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"幾時有室內版<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04dd12753aa91d52fd3feaff122cb27374302bc7","tid":1787111,"uid":282127,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"手機程式?又想靜雞雞呃人資料呃人位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc3f20358746dbbb3beb71a8592b4459ad6dfec","tid":1787111,"uid":247032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:14:31.000Z","msg":"係咪室內升旗d fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />著褲打飛機"},{"pid":"2eebd173063f9248c9d06dba2432602cfe484821","tid":1787111,"uid":200663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"咁同除夕煙花有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0631f29877eae06646bf33ae75d2e0819bce8d2","tid":1787111,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset